## Keybindings
bind M-g gotoline main
bind ^q exit main
bind ^w savefile main

bind ^s whereis main
bind ^r replace main
bind M-n findnext main
bind M-p findprevious main

bind ^y paste main
bind M-h chopwordleft main
bind M-d chopwordright main

bind M-m mark main
bind M-] indent main
bind M-[ unindent main
bind M-c comment main

bind M-b prevword main
bind M-f nextword main
bind M-n pagedown main
bind M-p pageup main
